Package: pixel-core
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, tcl8.4
Description: Core functionality of the Pixel framework
 Pixel is a Tcl extension that provides low level raster graphics functions,
 and through the use of helper modules allows loading and saving a large
 number of image formats, rendering True Type fonts, applying graphics filters
 and displaying to various targets, like SDL, Tk images, and so forth
